@BeforeSuit---> run before the <suite>
@AfterSuit-----> run after the </suite>

@BeforeTest------> run before <test>
@AfterTest-------> run after </test>


in order to configure reports for a xml file

--> goto run
--> edit configurations
--> select the xml file for which u want to enable the reports
--> click on listeners
---> click on add button
---> select email reportable
--> apply save
--> apply ok
